{
  "stem": "18932.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then we all marched to the ghetto, and my father got us an apartment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we took a lot of things with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We couldn't take too much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some clothes, some bedding, a couple of pots, I guess, pans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember, but maybe we did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, other people marched too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody marched toward the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No we just walked by ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a part of the Lodz that I was never before there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- this part was like poor part of Lodz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got an apartment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was one big room and a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had a grandmother, which was in a nursing home at that time in Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my mother took the-- her mother out and she lived with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, was the great hunger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had very little to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was rationed-- everything was rationed, like would get one ounce of kohlrabi and-- and maybe bread for a whole family for the whole week.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- but she stayed with us, till one day my father brought some horse meat that he got, because he worked for the-- for the-- he was an accountant in the ghetto [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he was able to get this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when she saw this and she said, my dear children, I can't stay with you anymore, because I cannot stay and eat this non-kosher food.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the nursing home was still in existence, so my father had to take her back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because my grandfather, when he passed on, he said to her, I don't want you to be-- you have eight children, but I never want you to be with any of them.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
